data.description: Fantastic property at a great pricein the highly desirable community of Spring Hill! 3 Nice Single-family Bedroom, 1 Full Bath situated in a fenced-in backyard. No HOA or CDD. When you walk in the front door you are greeted with the open and spacious living room and dining room which features a large sliding door, and vinyl floors. The kitchen has been remodeled and features stainless steel appliances, wood cabinets, a butcher countertop, a washer, and a dryer that were purchased in 2020. A/C was replaced in 2019 by previous owners. A new tankless water heater was installed in 2021. The home has a beautiful closed-in Lenai with windows and a screen where you can enjoy your morning coffee out there. Beautiful NEW light fixtures throughout the home. Excellent LOCATION. Easy access to highways, parks, springs, supermarkets, and pharmacies. COME SEE THIS HOME TODAY!
